<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs", {title: "Bartering System"}) %>

    <body>
        <div class="font2 bg" align="center">
            Welcome to the Bartering System
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <%- include("partials/navbar") %>
            <hr />
            <main class="my-5 font3">
                <!-- About -->
                <h1 align="center" id="About">Our Story</h1>
                <p class="my-5 lead">
                    Hi, We are the Vegetable Dog Team. Our batering system
                    website is located here. We have a great opportunity to
                    create our own website. Our adventure started with a common
                    goal: to try our best to make this website. We made this
                    concept a reality through countless cups of coffee,
                    brainstorming meetings, and late-night coding marathons. Our
                    platform is more than simply a website; it is a symbol of
                    our commitment, a manifestation of our enthusiasm, and —
                    most importantly — This has further deepened our
                    understanding of teamwork. We appreciate you coming along
                    for the journey. Together, let's trade, save, and sustain!
                </p>

                <!-- FAQs -->
                <h1 align="center" class="my-5" id="FAQs">FAQs</h1>
                <h4>Question: What is a batering system?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Answer: A batering system is an online platform where
                        users can exchange goods or services without the use of
                        money.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Question: How do I list my items for exchange?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Answer: You can list your items by creating an account,
                        logging in, and following the steps to upload the item
                        details and images.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Question: How do I find items I want to exchange for?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Answer: You can search for items using the search
                        function on the website, or you can browse through the
                        categories to find items that interest you.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Question: Is there a fee for using the batering system?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Answer: Our batering system is free to use for both
                        listing and exchanging items.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>
                    Question: How do I ensure my privacy when exchanging items?
                </h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Answer: Our platform allows you to exchange contact and
                        shipping information privately with the other party
                        involved in the trade.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <!-- Contact Us -->
                <h1 align="center" class="my-5" id="ContactUs">Contact Us</h1>
                <form
                    class="needs-validation"
                    action="/feedback"
                    method="post"
                    novalidate
                >
                    <h3>SEND US EMAIL</h3>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="Email" class="form-label"
                            >Email address</label
                        >
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            class="form-control"
                            id="Email"
                            name="email"
                            placeholder="name@example.com"
                            required
                        />
                        <div class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please enter a valid email address.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="Name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            class="form-control"
                            id="Name"
                            name="name"
                            required
                        />
                        <div class="invalid-feedback">
                            Name cannot be empty.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="Phone" class="form-label"
                            >Phone Number</label
                        >
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            class="form-control"
                            id="Phone"
                            name="phone"
                            placeholder="0400 000 000"
                            required
                        />
                        <div class="invalid-feedback"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="Text" class="form-label">Message</label>
                        <textarea
                            class="form-control"
                            id="Text"
                            name="message"
                            rows="4"
                        ></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div align="right">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark mb-3 col-12">
                            SEND
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </main>
        </div>
        <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
        <script
            src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"
            integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4="
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
        <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
        <script src="/js/navbar.js"></script>
    </body>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</html>
